body:
Seems like Jenkins build would not pickup changes in `Jenkinsfile` from a PR ([thread][1]) unless the PR is from a trusted source. For this PR that should have worked though.

@houshengbo Any way to test any change in Jenkins pipeline config?

[1]: https://support.cloudbees.com/hc/en-us/articles/227246367-Why-Jenkinsfile-changes-Are-Not-Reflected-in-PR-Build
